    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Decorating</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wallpaper or paint? Tiles or laminate? Floor lamps or sconces? The choice is yours! A wide range of decorative elements will allow you to create the desired atmosphere of the restaurant. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire employees or take them away from a competitor. Set up pay and work schedule. Raise the qualifications of your staff and unlock their potential. <br>Unlock new dishes and make the menu the way you see fit.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Purchases</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your cooks need ingredients and utensils, and your cleaners need chemistry. Keep track of the amount of goods in stock and buy new ones on time. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Problem situations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dialogue is the best way to avoid conflict. Deal with dissatisfied customers and make difficult decisions, but be prepared for unexpected results.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Promotion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From petty mischief to burglary: what can you do to ruin a rival restaurant's reputation? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Add the game to your wishlist so you don't miss the release!</strong> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375600/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.poster.avif?t=1728910843\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375600/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.webm?t=1728910843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375600/extras/dd9124abe6bf6bd35dcf2aaae8e252b0.mp4?t=1728910843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
